  "summary": "The dominant user needs are contacting DAB, selecting the correct division, and accessing phone/email/mailing details. The highest-risk failure is misrouting—users struggle to determine the right office, which can delay legal or appeals processes. Contact details themselves are easy to find, but decision-making is not well supported. Validation should focus on whether users can correctly identify their division and complete contact tasks without confusion. Improving decision guidance is likely the biggest UX gain."
